contributionDescription:
I believe that Superchain will contribute significantly to the convenience of our lives.
In anticipation of that, I support projects in the Superchain ecosystem and introduce them to people. Primarily active on Farcaster, Telegram and X. You can see my activity on my page.
impactDescription: I've been explaining SuperChain to a lot of people and getting a lot of positive results, and the response is that people are joining SuperChain projects. Recently, I've gotten a lot of people involved in BASE, ZORA, and Farcaster. I'm going to find different projects that are active within SuperChain and share them with people.
pwCategorySuggestions: Community Building, Information Sharing, Blockchain Education
